1 to 1 chat/file transfer

A, B: open client
B: "hey i'm listening on host:port, my pub key sig is AB:CD:..."
A: connect to host:port
B: sends public key
A: verifies key as given securely by B
A: sends session key encrypted with B's public key
B: decrypts session key using private key
B: sends confirmation to A encrypted with session key
A: initiates request...
A, B: make love over session-encrypted stream

